Nico.

248
00:18:34,014 --> 00:18:36,332
Ei, Eddy.

249
00:18:38,818 --> 00:18:40,186
O que foi?

250
00:18:45,792 --> 00:18:47,927
Ei, qual é o problema, cara?

251
00:18:50,964 --> 00:18:53,144
